## What to Expect When Buying a Home Here

When you're shopping for homes, don't just look at the list price. Ask your agent for the **current tax bill** on any property — and keep in mind it may go up after you purchase if the home was previously under a homestead cap.

As a rule of thumb, budget **1.9%–2.3% of purchase price per year** in property taxes for the Leander/Cedar Park area.

